                "invention-title": [
                    "Self-heating low-carbon direct reduction iron process",
                    "一种自热式低碳直接还原铁工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a self-heating low-carbon direct reduction iron process, which is used for preparing reduced iron or sponge iron and comprises the following steps of: pre-reducing an iron raw material containing iron oxide in a preheating section of an electric heating shaft kiln; and directly electrifying the iron raw material or a solid material (hereinafter referred to as the solid material) obtained by changing the iron raw material in the heating process through a power supply electrode in a heating section of the electric heating shaft kiln, heating the material through resistance heating of a solid material pile in the heating section, and providing reaction heat for an endothermic reaction of reducing iron oxide by the hydrogen-rich gas. The method has the advantages of simple process flow, low carbon emission, low investment and high production capacity."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种自热式低碳直接还原铁工艺，用以制备还原铁或海绵铁，是将含氧化铁的铁原料在电热竖窑预热段中预还原，然后在电热竖窑加热段中通过电源电极对该铁原料或其在所述的加热过程中变化所得的固体物料(以下称为固体物料)直接通电，通过处于加热段的固体物料料堆的电阻发热而加热物料并为富氢气体还原氧化铁的吸热反应提供反应热。本发明的优点是工艺流程简单、碳排放低、投资少、生产能力大。"
                }
            ]
